THIRD-PARTY CODE
================

This project contains code ported from, and is based on the work of, several
open source projects that are licensed under their own terms. See
THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES for full license texts and attribution.

  - dbanay/Smalltalk (MIT) — https://github.com/dbanay/Smalltalk
      Primary reference implementation. Object memory, BitBlt, interpreter,
      and primitive table are ported from this code base.

  - Xerox Smalltalk-80 virtual image (Xerox license) —
      http://www.wolczko.com/st80/image.tar.gz
      The virtual image itself is NOT redistributed with this software.
      Users fetch it separately under Xerox's original release terms.

  - Blue Book: "Smalltalk-80: The Language and its Implementation"
      by Adele Goldberg and David Robson (1983).
      This implementation follows the specifications in chapters 26–30.
